**Installation Process**
---First need to install prerequisites
mehedi@kali:~$ sudo apt install patch build-essential zlib1g-dev liblzma-dev ruby-dev
mehedi@kali:~$ gem install nokogiri
---Then
mehedi@kali:~$ gem install wpscan

Or
--Downloading from github
mehedi@kali:~$ git clone https://github.com/wpscanteam/wpscan
--Go to wpscan directory. If file is zip the unzip first
mehedi@kali:~$ cd wpscan/
--Then
mehedi@kali:~$ bundle install && rake install

